.row
  %h2 Matches
  .small-row
    Each of these awesome people is a good match for you - they speak a language you want to learn and you speak a language <em>they</em> want to learn! Go ahead and give them a "Friend", maybe you two can meet up soon to have a chat.
  - @matches.each do |user|
    - unless user == current_user
      .medium-4.columns
        .profile-card
          %i.fa.fa-user.profile-default-image
          .profile-info
            %h4.subheader
              = link_to user.name, home_path(user)
            %p= user.blurb
            %p
              %strong= user.location
              .language-box
                - unless user.language_list.empty?
                  .languages.padding-5
                    - user.language_list.each do |language|
                      %span.primary.label.medium-font
                        = language
                - unless user.learning_list.empty?
                  .learnings.padding-5
                    - user.learning_list.each do |learning|
                      %span.label.success.medium-font
                        = learning